	    <title id="subsystem_title">Installing the Application Server and File Server (using Subsystem)</title>
	    <section id="important_note">
	    <title id="title_important note">Important note</title>
	    <important id="downgradekernel">
        <para>
          Due to issues with the latest kernel, it's necessary to downgrade it. You have to use a Linux kernel version 3.2.0 in your host server
        </para>   
        </important>
        <itemizedlist> 
		<listitem>
        <para>
			Install the previous kernel
		<screen>
<![CDATA[# sudo apt-get install linux-image-3.2.0-59-virtual]]>
          </screen>          
        </para>  
        </listitem>
        <listitem>  
        <para>
		Remove the latest
		  <screen>
<![CDATA[# sudo apt-get remove linux-image-3.8.0]]>
          </screen>
        </para> 
        </listitem>
        <listitem>  
        <para>You must reboot the server now</para>
        </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>      
